Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那借来的写轮眼能抵挡这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识下真品与盗版的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视线…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 她怎么过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让卡卡西老师背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走的不是一条道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.02,0:00:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起努力过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经认为那就是自己该走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是决意踏上复仇之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我才活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法像你和鸣人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了佐助什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…求求你 留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想尽一切办法帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你和我一起留下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果实在不行 就带我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然…很讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我就喊人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来的真是时候啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你能过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助真的打算杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果鸣人没有赶来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我已经被佐助亲手杀死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱同是第七班的成员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是曾经的第七班…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 小樱 你们现在应该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他身上浮现的是真正的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经不是曾经的佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听阿飞那家伙说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼬的真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那家伙说的是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没父母也没兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的理解能有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道鸣人是怎么对你的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么流言蜚语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都一直视你为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便大家都准备对付佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人还是一心想着救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么救…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要把你…从复仇的泥泞中拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的复仇帷幕已经拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手刃了一个鼬的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到那只右手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀害了多少宇智波族人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出手的是鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你逼他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是里四象封印术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 快远离团藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这干掉了木叶的高层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫团藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助难道仅凭一人就打倒他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 从未有过的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被玷污的宇智波得到净化的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波从这腐朽的忍者世界超脱的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你们木叶长久以来的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你们所愿 让亘古以来一直被否定的宇智波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你们的记忆中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩断同木叶所有的羁绊才是净化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是宇智波的真正复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那憎恨累积而成的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造就了现在的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助也是这个时代的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人也好 小樱也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽不能确定 但多少也能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都给我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卡卡西老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里会看到不愿看到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 从静音那学来的毒苦无是杀不掉佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他继承了大蛇丸的免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你已经清楚自己的心意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我已经帮你恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续战斗可不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动 香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同人质的要害一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 这是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了 佐助的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓不愿看到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杀了佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽 我可不会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 或许…我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该反过来才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地逃啊 逃啊 苟且偷生下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后当有一天你拥有跟我相同的眼睛后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经被村民们厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为我体内的九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经也憎恨村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想过报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些涂鸦给我擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那小子 就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要将这种家伙留在村子里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三代替我们想想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋 滚一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然来一下你要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你好了 赶紧给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这样对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连班主任也用这种眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是扫把星或霉菌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会像你一样想着如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾觉得我会一直孤单下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到同你和伊鲁卡老师相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大智 吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不听话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过不准和那个孩子一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人…告诉你真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道十二年前封印妖狐的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后村里就有了条规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是条绝对不能让你知道的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只对我保密 什么规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能说出鸣人就是妖狐的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 你就是杀害了伊鲁卡的双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭村子的九尾妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所憧憬的四代火影将九尾封印在你体内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里所有人都瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会认同你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果再可靠些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不会经历这些痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走火入魔般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和伊鲁卡老师 我才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我知道你也总是一人时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你跟我一样我就觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背负着九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背负着宇智波的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们背负着相似的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天看到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实想去找你聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得你应该能理解我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问原因的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你什么都行 让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我决定把你当作我的竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就成了我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾在终结之谷说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的对决让我终于有所理解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也读懂我内心的真实想法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:23:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么对我如此执着